  correct_answer = 'D',
  explanation = 'Context shows the team''s first conclusion required revision after further trials. In that frame, "bolster" must fit an meaning of provisional or adjustable judgment rather than certainty. Choice D matches that nuance, while the others describe opposite or irrelevant senses.',
